=== 死亡率的所有成因 ===
初步發現維他命D<sub>3</sub>補充劑可降低老年人的死亡風險<ref name=Bj2014/><ref name=Aut2013/>，但效果尚未得到足夠明顯和足夠肯定使補充劑值得推薦<ref name=Futil2014/>。其他形式（維他命D<sub>2</sub>、阿法骨化醇和骨化三醇）似乎對死亡風險沒有任何有益的作用<ref name=Bj2014>{{cite journal | vauthors = Bjelakovic G, Gluud LL, Nikolova D, Whitfield K, Wetterslev J, Simonetti RG, Bjelakovic M, Gluud C | display-authors = 6 | title = Vitamin D supplementation for prevention of mortality in adults | journal = The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | pages = CD007470 | date = January 2014 | pmid = 24414552 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD007470.pub3 | type = Systematic review }}</ref>。血液中較高的水平似乎跟較低的死亡風險有關，但尚未清楚補充劑是否可以帶來這種益處<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Schöttker B, Jorde R, Peasey A, Thorand B, Jansen EH, Groot L, Streppel M, Gardiner J, Ordóñez-Mena JM, Perna L, Wilsgaard T, Rathmann W, Feskens E, Kampman E, Siganos G, Njølstad I, Mathiesen EB, Kubínová R, Pająk A, Topor-Madry R, Tamosiunas A, Hughes M, Kee F, Bobak M, Trichopoulou A, Boffetta P, Brenner H | display-authors = 6 | title = Vitamin D and mortality: meta-analysis of individual participant data from a large consortium of cohort studies from Europe and the United States | journal = BMJ | volume = 348 | issue = jun17 16 | pages = g3656 | date = June 2014 | pmid = 24938302 | pmc = 4061380 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.g3656 | author28 = Consortium on Health Ageing: Network of Cohorts in Europe the United States }}</ref>。過量及缺乏維他命D都會導致身體功能異常和過早衰老<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Tuohimaa P | s2cid = 40625040 | title = Vitamin D and aging | journal = The Journal of Steroid Biochemistry and Molecular Biology | volume = 114 | issue = 1–2 | pages = 78–84 | date = March 2009 | pmid = 19444937 | doi = 10.1016/j.jsbmb.2008.12.020 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Tuohimaa P, Keisala T, Minasyan A, Cachat J, Kalueff A | s2cid = 17462970 | title = Vitamin D, nervous system and aging | journal = Psychoneuroendocrinology | volume = 34 Suppl 1 | pages = S278-86 | date = December 2009 | pmid = 19660871 | doi = 10.1016/j.psyneuen.2009.07.003 }}</ref><ref name="pmid20590845">{{cite journal | vauthors = Manya H, Akasaka-Manya K, Endo T | title = Klotho protein deficiency and aging | journal = Geriatrics & Gerontology International | volume = 10 Suppl 1 | issue = Suppl 1 | pages = S80-7 | date = July 2010 | pmid = 20590845 | doi = 10.1111/j.1447-0594.2010.00596.x }}</ref>。血清降鈣素水平與死亡率的所有成因之間的關係是呈拋物線的<ref name="Ross_2011"/>。在黑色人口中出現維他命D含量較低的維他命D危害似乎較低於白色人口<ref name="Ross_2011" />。

== 維他命D過量 ==
{{main|{{le|維他命D毒性|Vitamin D toxicity}}}}
維他命D毒性很少<ref name="Holick_2007" />，這是由於高劑量的維他命D補充劑而非陽光引致的。維他命D毒性的下限尚未確定；然而根據一些研究，對於9-71歲的年齡組別的最高容許攝入量（UL）為每天4,000 [[國際單位|IU]]（每天100 µg）<ref name="RossetalAJCE2011">{{cite journal | vauthors = Ross AC, Manson JE, Abrams SA, Aloia JF, Brannon PM, Clinton SK, Durazo-Arvizu RA, Gallagher JC, Gallo RL, Jones G, Kovacs CS, Mayne ST, Rosen CJ, Shapses SA | display-authors = 6 | title = The 2011 report on dietary reference intakes for calcium and vitamin D from the Institute of Medicine: what clinicians need to know | journal = The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology and Metabolism | volume = 96 | issue = 1 | pages = 53–8 | date = January 2011 | pmid = 21118827 | pmc = 3046611 | doi = 10.1210/jc.2010-2704 }}</ref>，而其他研究得出的結論是，在健康的成年人中，持續攝入超過每天1,250μg（50,000 IU）可在幾個月後產生明顯的[[毒性|毒性]]，並可以增加血清25-羥基維他命D水平增加至150 ng/mL或更高<ref name="Holick_2007"/><ref name="Merck" />。那些患有某些疾病，例如原發性[[副甲狀腺功能亢進症|副甲狀腺功能亢進症]]<ref name="Vieth"/>對維他命D更加敏感，並為了應對維他命D營養增加時會產生[[高血鈣|高血鈣]]症，而孕婦在懷孕期間的高鈣血症可能會增加對維他命D作用的胎兒敏感性，及智力低下綜合症和臉部畸形<ref name="Vieth"/><ref>{{cite book |title=Tolerable Upper Intake Limits for Vitamins And Minerals |publisher=[[European_Food_Safety_Authority|European Food Safety Authority]] |date=December 2006 |isbn=978-92-9199-014-6 |url=http://www.efsa.europa.eu/en/home/oldsc/upper_level_opinions_full-part33.pdf |access-date=2020-08-18 |archive-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506143914/http://www.efsa.europa.eu/en/home/oldsc/upper_level_opinions_full-part33.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

突發性嬰兒高鈣血症（Idiopathic infantile hypercalcemia）是由於[[CYP24A1|CYP24A1]]的基因突變引致的，導致這種基因突變的嬰兒減少對維他命D的降解。患有這種基因突變的嬰兒對維他命D的敏感性增加，如果額外攝入的話會有發生高鈣血症的風險<ref name="pmid21675912">{{cite journal | vauthors = Schlingmann KP, Kaufmann M, Weber S, Irwin A, Goos C, John U, Misselwitz J, Klaus G, Kuwertz-Bröking E, Fehrenbach H, Wingen AM, Güran T, Hoenderop JG, Bindels RJ, Prosser DE, Jones G, Konrad M | display-authors = 6 | title = Mutations in CYP24A1 and idiopathic infantile hypercalcemia | journal = The New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 365 | issue = 5 | pages = 410–21 | date = August 2011 | pmid = 21675912 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1056/NEJMoa1103864 }}</ref><ref name="pmid31188746">{{cite journal | vauthors = De Paolis E, Scaglione GL, De Bonis M, Minucci A, Capoluongo E | title = CYP24A1 and SLC34A1 genetic defects associated with idiopathic infantile hypercalcemia: from genotype to phenotype | journal = Clinical Chemistry and Laboratory Medicine | volume = 57 | issue = 11 | pages = 1650–1667 | date = October 2019 | pmid = 31188746 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1515/cclm-2018-1208 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。這種紊亂可以持續到成年<ref name="pmid27588937">{{cite journal | vauthors = Tebben PJ, Singh RJ, Kumar R | title = Vitamin D-Mediated Hypercalcemia: Mechanisms, Diagnosis, and Treatment | journal = Endocrine Reviews | volume = 37 | issue = 5 | pages = 521–547 | date = October 2016 | pmid = 27588937 | pmc = 5045493 | doi = 10.1210/er.2016-1070 }}</ref>。

2015年發表的一篇評論指出，僅在25（OH）D血清濃度高於200 nmol/L時才報告有不良反應<ref name="pmid26288575">{{cite journal | vauthors = Dahlquist DT, Dieter BP, Koehle MS | title = Plausible ergogenic effects of vitamin D on athletic performance and recovery | journal = Journal of the International Society of Sports Nutrition | volume = 12 | issue =  | pages = 33 | year = 2015 | pmid = 26288575 | pmc = 4539891 | doi = 10.1186/s12970-015-0093-8 | type = Review }}</ref>。已知的涉及高鈣血症的已公佈毒性病例（其中已知的維他命D劑量和25-羥基維他命D水平為已知所有每天攝入≥40,000 IU（1,000 μg）<ref name=Vieth/>。

孕婦或哺乳期婦女在服用維他命D補充劑之前應諮詢醫生。FDA建議維他命D液體補充劑的製造商應清晰準確地將這些產品隨附的滴管標記為400 IU（1 IU為25 ng膽鈣化固醇/麥角鈣化固醇的生物等效物）。此外，對於用於嬰兒的產品，FDA建議滴管的容量不能超過400 IU<ref name="url_FDA_Caution_Vitamin_D_for_Infants">{{cite press release |url=https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm215150.htm |title=FDA Cautions on Accurate Vitamin D Supplementation for Infants |date=June 15, 2010 |publisher=Food and Drug Administration (FDA) |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/7993/20170112002746/https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm215150.htm |archive-date=2017-01-12 |url-status=dead |access-date=2020-08-18 |dead-url=no }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。對於嬰兒（由出生起至12個月），其允許的上限（無傷害的最大可以忍受量）設定為每天25 μg（1,000 IU）。對嬰兒來說，每天1,000mg的話，在一個月內會產生毒性<ref name="Merck">{{MerckManual|01|004|k||Vitamin D}}</ref>。受加拿大和美國政府委託，{{le|國家醫學科學院|National Academy of Medicine}}（IoM）{{as of|2010|11|30|lc=y}}已將1至3歲年齡段的容許上限（UL）增加至每天2,500 IU，4至8歲的兒童每天3,000 IU，而9-71歲以上則是每天4,000 IU（包括了孕婦或哺乳期婦女）<ref name="RossetalAJCE2011"/>。

骨化三醇本身以[[負反饋|負反饋]]周期自動調節，並且受到[[副甲狀腺激素|副甲狀腺激素]]、{{le|成纖維細胞生長因子23|Fibroblast growth factor 23}}、[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]、鈣質和磷酸鹽的影響<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Olmos-Ortiz A, Avila E, Durand-Carbajal M, Díaz L | title = Regulation of calcitriol biosynthesis and activity: focus on gestational vitamin D deficiency and adverse pregnancy outcomes | journal = Nutrients | volume = 7 | issue = 1 | pages = 443–80 | date = January 2015 | pmid = 25584965 | pmc = 4303849 | doi = 10.3390/nu7010443 }}</ref>。

=== 過量的影響 ===
維他命D過量會引致高鈣血症，這是維他命D毒性的強烈顯示 — 透過排尿和口渴的增加可以注意到這一點。若高鈣血症不獲處理，其結果會引致鈣質於軟組織和器官（如腎臟，肝臟和心臟）有過量的沉積，最後導致疼痛和器官損傷<ref name="Holick_2007"/><ref name="Brown_2008"/><ref name="Insel_2006">{{cite book |first1=Paul |last1=Insel |first2=Don |last2=Ross |first3=Melissa |last3=Bernstein |first4=Kimberley |last4=McMahon | name-list-format = vanc |title=Discovering Nutrition |url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=6IWHCgAAQBAJ}}|date=2015-03-18|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|isbn=978-1-284-06465-0}}</ref>。

維他命D過量的主要症狀都是高鈣血症的症狀，包括[[食欲不振|食欲不振]]、噁心和嘔吐。這些可能隨後是[[多尿症|多尿症]]、{{le|劇渴|Polydipsia}}、虛弱、失眠、緊張、[[癢|痕癢]]，最後是[[腎衰竭|腎衰竭]]。此外，它有可能發展為[[蛋白尿|蛋白尿]]、[[管型_(尿液)|管型尿液]]、{{le|氮質血症|Azotemia}}及{{le|轉移性鈣化|Metastatic calcification}}（尤其出現於腎臟）<ref name="Merck" />。維他命D毒性的其他症狀包括幼兒智力低下、骨骼異常生長和形成、腹瀉、易怒、體重減輕和嚴重抑鬱<ref name="Holick_2007"/><ref name="Insel_2006"/>。

維他命D毒性可透過停止維他命D補充劑並限制鈣的攝入來處理。腎臟損害可能是不可逆轉的。長時間暴露於陽光下通常不會引起維他命D毒性。在皮膚中產生的維他命D前體的濃度達到[[化學平衡|化學平衡]]，並且產生的任何進一步的維他命D都會被降解<ref name="Vieth">{{cite journal | vauthors = Vieth R | title = Vitamin D supplementation, 25-hydroxyvitamin D concentrations, and safety | journal = The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition | volume = 69 | issue = 5 | pages = 842–56 | date = May 1999 | pmid = 10232622 | doi = 10.1093/ajcn/69.5.842 | url = http://www.ajcn.org/content/69/5/842.full.pdf | access-date = 2020-08-18 | archive-date = 2012-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120703210532/http://www.ajcn.org/content/69/5/842.full.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 生物合成 ==
自然界中維他命D的合成取決於紫外線輻射的存在，以及隨後在肝臟和腎臟中的活化。許多動物從[[7-脫氫膽固醇|7-脫氫膽固醇]]合成維他命D<sub>3</sub>，許多真菌從[[麥角固醇|麥角固醇]]合成維生素D<sub>2</sub><ref name="pmid1297827">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF | title = Evolutionary biology and pathology of vitamin D | journal = Journal of Nutritional Science and Vitaminology | volume = Spec No | issue =  | pages = 79–83 | year = 1992 | pmid = 1297827 | doi = 10.3177/jnsv.38.Special_79 | url = https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jnsv1973/38/Special/38_Special_79/_pdf | doi-access = free | access-date = 2020-08-19 | archive-date = 2020-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201222015713/https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jnsv1973/38/Special/38_Special_79/_pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="keegan"/>。

=== 光化學 ===
[[File:Vitamin_D_biosynthesis_in_fungi_and_animals.svg|thumb]]
[[File:Calcitriol-Biosynthese_2.svg|thumb]]至維生素D<sub>3</sub>的熱異構化。]]
把7-脫氫膽固醇轉化為維他命D<sub>3</sub>的轉化過程涉及兩個步驟<ref name="pmid3030826">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF | title = Photosynthesis of vitamin D in the skin: effect of environmental and life-style variables | journal = Federation Proceedings | volume = 46 | issue = 5 | pages = 1876–82 | date = April 1987 | pmid = 3030826 | doi =  }}</ref><ref name="pmid24466410">{{cite journal | vauthors = Deluca HF | title = History of the discovery of vitamin D and its active metabolites | journal = BoneKEy Reports | volume = 3 | issue =  | pages = 479 | date = January 2014 | pmid = 24466410 | pmc = 3899558 | doi = 10.1038/bonekey.2013.213 }}</ref>：首先，7-脫氫膽固醇在6-電子[[順旋/對旋|順旋/對旋]]開環[[電環化反應|電環化反應]]中被紫外線以[[光分解作用|光分解作用]]光解；其產物為[[前维生素D3|前維生素D<sub>3</sub>]]。其次，維他命原D<sub>3</sub>自發地[[同分異構|同分異構]]至維生素D<sub>3</sub>（[[膽鈣化醇|膽鈣化醇]]），在[[σ遷移反應#例子|σ遷移反應]]中的{{le|異面與同面|Antarafacial and suprafacial}}。在室溫下，維生素原D<sub>3</sub>在有機溶劑中向維生素D<sub>3</sub>的轉化大約需要12天才能完成。皮膚中維他命原D<sub>3</sub>向維他命D<sub>3</sub>的轉化比有機溶劑中快約10倍<ref name="Holick_2004" />。

麥角固醇向維他命D<sub>2</sub>的轉化遵循相似的過程，透過光解形成維生素原D<sub>2</sub>，因而會異構化成維生素D<sub>2</sub><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Eyley |first1=Stephen C. |last2=Williams |first2=Dudley H. | name-list-format = vanc |title=Photolytic production of vitamin D. The preparative value of a photo-sensitiser |journal=Journal of the Chemical Society, Chemical Communications |date=1975 |issue=20 |pages=858a |doi=10.1039/C3975000858A}}</ref>。維他命原D<sub>2</sub>在甲醇中向維他命D<sub>2</sub>的轉化速率與維他命原D<sub>3</sub>相約。此過程於白色蘑菇中會更快<ref name="keegan" />{{rp|at=fig. 3}}。

=== 皮膚合成 ===
[[File:Skinlayers_zh.png|thumb]]
在大多數脊椎動物的皮膚中（包括人類）<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=12514284 |year=2003 |last1=Crissey |first1=SD |last2=Ange |first2=KD |last3=Jacobsen |first3=KL |last4=Slifka |first4=KA |last5=Bowen |first5=PE |last6=Stacewicz-Sapuntzakis |first6=M |last7=Langman |first7=CB |last8=Sadler |first8=W |last9=Kahn |first9=S |title=Serum concentrations of lipids, vitamin D metabolites, retinol, retinyl esters, tocopherols and selected carotenoids in twelve captive wild felid species at four zoos |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-nutrition_2003-01_133_1/page/160 |volume=133 |issue=1 |pages=160–6 |journal=The Journal of nutrition}}</ref>，而裸鼴鼠似乎生來缺乏膽骨化醇<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=8384476 |year=1993 |last1=Yahav |first1=S |last2=Buffenstein |first2=R |title=Cholecalciferol supplementation alters gut function and improves digestibility in an underground inhabitant, the naked mole rat (Heterocephalus glaber), when fed on a carrot diet |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-nutrition_1993-01_69_1/page/233 |volume=69 |issue=1 |pages=233–41 |journal=The British journal of nutrition |doi=10.1079/BJN19930025}}</ref>，因為其血液中檢測不到25（OH）D，對某些動物來說，其厚厚的毛皮阻擋了紫外線，而這些鳥獸也有自己的辦法，牠們把7-脫氫膽固醇分泌到毛皮表面，合成維他命D<sub>3</sub>後再自己舔回肚子裡<ref>{{cite book |first1=Sam D. |last1=Stout |first2=Sabrina C. |last2=Agarwal |last3=Stout |first3=Samuel D. |title=Bone loss and osteoporosis: an anthropological perspective |publisher=Kluwer Academic/Plenum Publishers |location=New York |year=2003 |isbn=0-306-47767-X}}</ref>。

維他命D<sub>3</sub>是由7-脫氫膽固醇以光化學方式產生的<ref name="pmid12514284">{{cite journal | vauthors = Crissey SD, Ange KD, Jacobsen KL, Slifka KA, Bowen PE, Stacewicz-Sapuntzakis M, Langman CB, Sadler W, Kahn S, Ward A | display-authors = 6 | title = Serum concentrations of lipids, vitamin d metabolites, retinol, retinyl esters, tocopherols and selected carotenoids in twelve captive wild felid species at four zoos | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-nutrition_2003-01_133_1/page/160 | journal = The Journal of Nutrition | volume = 133 | issue = 1 | pages = 160–6 | date = January 2003 | pmid = 12514284 | doi = 10.1093/jn/133.1.160 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。維他命D<sub>3</sub>的前體，7-脫氫膽固醇的產量相對較高。7-脫氫膽固醇在290-315 nm的[[波長|波長]]下跟[[紫外線#科學上的分類|UVB光]]產生反應<ref>{{cite book |isbn=978-0-12-809965-0 |first=Michael F. |last=Holick |chapter=Chapter 4: Photobiology of Vitamin D |title=Vitamin D: Volume 1: Biochemistry, Physiology and Diagnostics |edition=4th |publisher=Academic Press |place=London, UK|editor-last1=Feldman|editor-first1=David|editor-last2=Wesley Pike|editor-first2=J.|editor-last3=Bouillon|editor-first3=Roger|editor-last4=Giovannucci|editor-first4=Edward|editor-last5=Goltzman|editor-first5=David|editor-last6=Hewison|editor-first6=Martin |date=2018| name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>。這些波長不僅存在於太陽光中，而且存在於[[室內曬黑|室內曬黑]]中的紫外線燈發出的光（那是主要在[[紫外線#科學上的分類|UVA]]的光譜中產生紫外線，但通常會產生UVB總量的4％至10％）。透過窗戶暴露的陽光不足，因為玻璃幾乎會完全阻擋了UVB的光線<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/17/science/17qna.html |title=Q&A Sunshine Vitamin D |first=C. Claiborne |last=Ray |name-list-format=vanc |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2005-05-17 |access-date=2013-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221030710/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/17/science/17qna.html |archive-date=2013-02-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=iuva>{{cite web |url=http://iuva.org/uv-faqs |title=UV FAQs |vauthors=Bolton J |publisher=International Ultraviolet Association |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530132909/http://iuva.org/uv-faqs |archive-date=2013-05-30 |accessdate=2020-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

面部、手臂和腿部的皮膚適量地暴露於陽光下，可以產生足夠分量的維他命D，而每星期兩次，每次平均5–30分鐘，又或大約25％的時間，可將曬傷程度降至最低。皮膚顏色越深，日光越微弱，則需要暴露的時間越長。暴露在紫外線下不可能引致維他命D過量：皮膚達到平衡時，該維他命降解的速度與其產生的速度一樣快<ref name="Holick_2007"/><ref>{{cite journal |author=Holick MF |s2cid=87725403 |date=February 2002 |title=Vitamin D: the underappreciated D-lightful hormone that is important for skeletal and cellular health |journal=Current Opinion in Endocrinology, Diabetes and Obesity |volume=9 |issue=1 |pages=87–98 |doi=10.1097/00060793-200202000-00011}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF | title = Sunlight and vitamin D: both good for cardiovascular health | journal = Journal of General Internal Medicine | volume = 17 | issue = 9 | pages = 733–5 | date = September 2002 | pmid = 12220371 | pmc = 1495109 | doi = 10.1046/j.1525-1497.2002.20731.x }}</ref>。

[[防曬油|防曬油]]把紫外線吸收或反射，並防止大部分紫外線到達皮膚<ref name=holick87/>。根據UVB光譜得出的防曬係數（SPF）為8的防曬霜可使維他命D的合成能力降低95％，而SPF 15則使其降低98％<ref name="Ross_2011">{{cite book |author=Institute of Medicine (IoM) |chapter=8, Implications and Special Concerns |chapterurl=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK56078/ |veditors=Ross AC, Taylor CL, Yaktine AL, Del Valle HB |title=Dietary Reference Intakes for Calcium and Vitamin D |publisher=National Academies Press |year=2011 |isbn=978-0-309-16394-1 |pmid=21796828 |doi=10.17226/13050 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK56070/ |series=The National Academies Collection: Reports funded by National Institutes of Health |access-date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126052042/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK56070/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

皮膚由兩個主要層級組成：主要由[[結締組織|結締組織]]組成，稱為[[真皮|真皮]]的內層，以及外面比較薄的[[表皮_(皮膚)|表皮]]<ref name="nci">{{cite web |url=https://training.seer.cancer.gov/melanoma/anatomy/ |title=Anatomy of the skin |publisher=National Cancer Institute, US National Institutes of Health, Bethesda |date=2016 |access-date=2016-12-19 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128090055/https://training.seer.cancer.gov/melanoma/anatomy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。厚表皮包括了手掌和腳底的五個層級組成，從外到內，它們是：[[角質層|角質層]]、[[透明層|透明層]]、[[顆粒層|顆粒層]]、[[棘層|棘層]]和[[基底層|基底層]]；維他命D於兩個最內層中產生[[角質形成細胞|角質形成細胞]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Vitamin D and Skin Health |url=http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/mic/health-disease/skin-health/vitamin-D |website=LINUS PAULING INSTITUTE Micronutrient Information Center |publisher=Oregon State University |access-date=2017-03-30 |date=2016-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129113936/https://lpi.oregonstate.edu/mic/health-disease/skin-health/vitamin-D |dead-url=no }}</ref>，分別是基底層和棘層<ref name="holick87">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF, Smith E, Pincus S | title = Skin as the site of vitamin D synthesis and target tissue for 1,25-dihydroxyvitamin D3. Use of calcitriol (1,25-dihydroxyvitamin D3) for treatment of psoriasis | journal = Archives of Dermatology | volume = 123 | issue = 12 | pages = 1677–1683a | date = December 1987 | pmid = 2825606 | doi = 10.1001/archderm.1987.01660360108022 }}</ref>。

7-脫氫膽固醇在波長在270-300納米（峰值295-297納米）之間的紫外線照射下可以變構轉化為維他命D<sub>3</sub><ref name="Hume Lucas Smith 1927 362-367">{{cite journal |first1=Eleanor Margaret |last1=Hume |first2=Nathaniel Sampson |last2=Lucas |first3=Hannah Henderson |last3=Smith |title=On the Absorption of Vitamin D from the Skin |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_biochemical-journal_1927_21_2/page/362 |journal=Biochemical Journal |volume=21 |issue=2 |pages=362–367 |year=1927 |pmid=16743844 |pmc=1251921}}</ref>，在陽光中的紫外線指數（夜間的紫外線指數為0，熱帶、高原地區、晴天時的紫外線指數為15），＞3的時候或在日光浴燈下才會有這種能發揮作用的紫外線。日光浴燈產生的紫外線大多數是長波的UVA，而產生維他命D<sub>3</sub>所需要的是中波紫外線（UVB）佔其中的4-10%，從地域上說，熱帶地區的人每天都可以產生維他命D<sub>3</sub>，溫帶地區的人在春夏季節時也可以，而極地地區的人們，該處的紫外線強度幾乎不可能使其產生維他命D<sub>3</sub><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=13050&page=104 |title=Dietary Reference Intakes for Calcium and Vitamin D (2011)Page 104 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2015-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118070350/http://www.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=13050&page=104 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。血清25（OH）D的平均濃度的差異似乎應該隨緯度升高而降低，然而實際上並不跟預期的一致，例如在夏天，加拿大北部地區的日照強度與時間加起來比赤道地區的還要強，而且高緯度地區的生物於春夏季或秋季都有可能形成並儲存足夠的維他命D，UVB產生的維他命D功能（無法控制非酶促反應的異構作用）非常強大，以至於皮膚形成多餘的維他命D<sub>3</sub>必須及時降解掉，以免其產生毒性，最終使維他命D的合成和降解達到了平衡的狀態<ref name="Holick M 1995 638S–645S">{{cite journal |author=Holick MF |title=Environmental factors that influence the cutaneous production of vitamin D |journal=[[The_American_Journal_of_Clinical_Nutrition|The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition]] |volume=61 |issue=3 Suppl |pages=638S–645S |pmid=7879731 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/content/61/3/638S.full.pdf |date=March 1995 |access-date=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2012-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703210504/http://www.ajcn.org/content/61/3/638S.full.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 身體合成 ===
維他命D透過血流輸送到肝臟，在那裏轉化為激素前體骨化二醇，循環中的骨化二醇在腎臟和單核巨噬細胞系統中轉化為骨化三醇，從而成為具有生物活性的維他命D，而在免疫系統中，骨化三醇（1,25(OH)D）發揮着細胞因子的作用，保護機體抵抗微生物入侵<ref name="Adams&Hewison2010">{{cite journal |last1=Adams |first1=J. S. |last2=Hewison |first2=M. |title=Update in Vitamin D |journal=Journal of Clinical Endocrinology & Metabolism |volume=95 |issue=2 |pages=471–8 |year=2010 |pmid=20133466 |pmc=2840860 |doi=10.1210/jc.2009-1773}}</ref>。腎臟將骨化二醇轉化為骨化三醇釋放到血液中，跟維他命的結合蛋白結合，轉送到靶器官<ref name="River" />。骨化三醇透過激活維他命D受體發揮生物學效應，VDR存在於靶細胞表面<ref name="River" />的活化VDR可以作為轉錄因子，調節運載蛋白（如TRPV6和[[鈣結合蛋白|鈣結合蛋白]]）的表達，從而參與小腸內鈣的吸收<ref name=Bouillon2003 />。VDR屬於核受體中類固醇／甲狀腺素受體超級家族，可以在大多數器官中表達，包括腦部、心臟、皮膚、前列腺和乳腺等，VDR在小腸、骨骼、腎臟和甲狀旁腺的表達能夠保證血鈣血磷代謝正常（這與甲狀旁腺激素和降鈣素協同作用），並可以維持正常骨的質量<ref name="Sun">{{cite journal |pmid=15585788 |year=2004 |last1=Holick |first1=MF |title=Sunlight and vitamin D for bone health and prevention of autoimmune diseases, cancers, and cardiovascular disease |volume=80 |issue=6 Suppl |pages=1678S–88S |journal=[[The_American_Journal_of_Clinical_Nutrition|The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition]] |url=http://www.ajcn.org/content/80/6/1678S.long |access-date=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2012-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820061406/http://www.ajcn.org/content/80/6/1678S.long |dead-url=no }}</ref>。維他命D提高了腎上腺髓質細胞酪氨酸羥化酶的表達，也參與了神經營養因子、一氧化氮等物質的合成，並能提高機體穀胱甘肽的水平<ref name="pmid9011759" />。現在有意見認為VDR也干預了細胞增殖和分化，而且對免疫系統也起了很強的免疫促進作用，很多種白血球細胞包括單核細胞、T細胞、B細胞都能夠表達VDR<ref name="PDR" />。VDR除了可以激活某些基因外，還有其他一些作用機理已經闡明，其中一個非常重要效果是，它可以抑制刺蝟激素（一種參與器官形成的激素）的信號轉導<ref name=Sarkar2010>{{cite journal |author=Sarkar FH, Li Y, Wang Z, Kong D. |title=The role of nutraceuticals in the regulation of Wnt and Hedgehog signaling in cancer |journal=Cancer Metastasis Reviews |year=2010 |volume=29 |issue=3 |pages=383–64 |pmid=20711635 |pmc=2974632}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/713649_3 |title=Hedgehog signaling and Vitamin D |publisher=Medscape.com |date=2009-12-18 |accessdate=2010-03-25 |archive-date=2013-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511140755/http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/713649_3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

維他命D最重要的功能就是保持骨骼中鈣質的平衡，它可以增強小腸對鈣質的吸收、提高破骨細胞的數量和增強骨吸收、維持血鈣及血磷濃度以維持正常骨量，並調整甲狀旁腺激素來維持血鈣平衡。缺乏維他命D會引致鈣磷代謝異常，導致骨質密度降低、骨質流失（骨質疏鬆症），甚至是骨折。

=== 演化 ===
維他命D只能透過光化學過程合成。海洋中的浮游植物（例如[[鈣板金藻|鈣板金藻]]和[[赫氏圓石藻|赫氏圓石藻]]）已經超過5億年以來都是一直利用紫外線進行光合作用來合成維他命D。海洋中的原始脊椎動物可以把海洋中的鈣質吸收到其骨骼中，並食用富含維他命D的浮游生物來吸收該種維他命。

陸地上的脊椎動物已經超過3.5億年來以光合作用合成維他命D<ref name="isbn0-452-29688-9">{{cite book |url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=P4xbcP19H0AC  |pages = 27}}|title=The Vitamin D Solution: A 3-Step Strategy to Cure Our Most Common Health Problems|last=Holick|first=Michael F.|date=2010-04-01|publisher=Penguin Publishing Group|isbn=978-1-101-22293-5| name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>。
牠們的鈣化骨骼需要植物以外的另一種維他命D來源。牠們必須攝取它，或暴露於陽光下才能在皮膚中進行光合作用<ref name="pmid1297827"/><ref name="Holick_2004">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF | title = Vitamin D: importance in the prevention of cancers, type 1 diabetes, heart disease, and osteoporosis | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-clinical-nutrition_2004-03_79_3/page/362 | journal = The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition | volume = 79 | issue = 3 | pages = 362–71 | date = March 2004 | pmid = 14985208 | doi = 10.1093/ajcn/79.3.362 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。對於硬骨類脊椎動物來說，離開富含鈣質的海水來到陸地上，維他命D對保證其骨骼中的鈣質來說非常重要，由於維他命D的合成必須要有紫外線參與，所以早期登陸岸上的的脊椎動物必須把身體暴露於陽光下或者補充富含維他命D的食物來滿足其身體對維他命D的需求<ref name="Holick_2004" />。

在鳥類和帶有皮毛的哺乳類動物中，皮毛或羽毛會阻擋紫外線到達皮膚。相反，維他命D是由沉積於其羽毛或皮毛上皮膚的油性分泌物產生的，在修飾過程中通過口服獲得該種維他命<ref name="AgarwalStout2011">{{cite book |first1=Sabrina C. |last1=Agarwal |first2=Samuel D. |last2=Stout | name-list-format = vanc |title=Bone Loss and Osteoporosis: An Anthropological Perspective |url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=_JV3BQAAQBAJ}}|date=2011-06-28|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-1-4419-8891-1 |quote=從猿類和猴子的生物學角度來看，可以理解其高25(OH)D濃度和相對較高的維他命D需求量是可以理解的—-牠們的身體表面面積通常相對於人類來說質量較大，而且牠們都是精通梳理毛髮的動物，經其口腔消耗從皮毛分泌的油脂中產生的維他命D。儘管人類皮膚中產生的許多維他命D被直接吸收，但鳥類和有毛皮的動物在梳理毛髮的時候，會從口腔獲得大部分維他命D（1946年—Bicknell和Prescott；1999年—Carpenter和Zhao）。維他命D是由皮膚油脂分泌到皮毛中產生的。口服的紫外線暴露的皮膚分泌物是許多動物獲取維他命D「營養素」的方式。儘管弗雷澤（Fraser，1983）認為皮膚吸收維他命D可能更自然，但從動物身上讓我們知道，口服維他命D具有同樣的生理意義。由於可以從暴露於紫外線的人體汗液和皮膚分泌物，也可以認為早期人類也可以透過舔皮膚經口腔獲得的某些維他命D。|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060129105712/http://www.direct-ms.org/pdf/VitDVieth/Vieth%20Anthropology%20vit%20D.pdf |archive-date=2006-01-29 |url-status=live}}</ref>。然而，由於無法檢測到血清中25-OH維他命D水平，因此某些動物（如[[裸鼴鼠|裸鼴鼠]]），是天然膽鈣化醇缺乏症的動物<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Yahav S, Buffenstein R | title = Cholecalciferol supplementation alters gut function and improves digestibility in an underground inhabitant, the naked mole rat (Heterocephalus glaber), when fed on a carrot diet | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-nutrition_1993-01_69_1/page/233 | journal = The British Journal of Nutrition | volume = 69 | issue = 1 | pages = 233–41 | date = January 1993 | pmid = 8384476 | doi = 10.1079/BJN19930025 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。

=== 工業合成 ===
維他命D<sub>3</sub>（膽鈣化固醇）的生產是通過將[[7-脫氫膽固醇|7-脫氫膽固醇]]暴露於UVB光下，然後進行純化來生產的<ref name="Holick05">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF | title = The vitamin D epidemic and its health consequences | journal = The Journal of Nutrition | volume = 135 | issue = 11 | pages = 2739S–48S | date = November 2005 | pmid = 16251641 | doi = 10.1093/jn/135.11.2739S | url = http://jn.nutrition.org/content/135/11/2739S.full.pdf | quote = [Vitamin D3] is produced commercially by extracting 7-dehydrocholesterol from wool fat, followed by UVB irradiation and purification [...] [Vitamin D2] is commercially made by irradiating and then purifying the ergosterol extracted from yeast | access-date = 2012-01-02 | archive-date = 2017-11-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171118043538/http://jn.nutrition.org/content/135/11/2739S.full.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。7-脫氫膽固醇是魚類器官特別是肝臟中的天然物質<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Takeuchi A, Okano T, Sayamoto M, Sawamura S, Kobayashi T, Motosugi M, Yamakawa T | title = Tissue distribution of 7-dehydrocholesterol, vitamin D3 and 25-hydroxyvitamin D3 in several species of fishes | journal = Journal of Nutritional Science and Vitaminology | volume = 32 | issue = 1 | pages = 13–22 | date = February 1986 | pmid = 3012050 | doi = 10.3177/jnsv.32.13 | url = https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jnsv1973/32/1/32_1_13/_pdf | doi-access = free | access-date = 2020-08-20 | archive-date = 2018-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181101013656/https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jnsv1973/32/1/32_1_13/_pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，或廣泛存在於綿羊的羊毛脂（[[綿羊油|綿羊油]]）以及其他動物毛髮中的天然物質。

維他命D<sub>2</sub>（麥角鈣化醇）的生產方法也類似，利用酵母或蘑菇中的麥角甾醇作為起始原材料<ref name="Holick05"/><ref name=keegan/>。

