== 作用機理 ==
=== 代謝活化 ===
[[File:Cholecalciferol_to_calcidiol_CH3.svg|thumb]]至{{le|骨化二醇|Calcifediol}}的肝臟羥基化。]]
[[File:Calcidiol_to_calcitriol_CH3.svg|thumb]]的腎臟羥基化。]]
維他命D通過血流輸送到肝臟，它在這裡被轉化為前激素降鈣素，然後循環中的骨化二醇可在腎臟中轉化為骨化三醇，那是腎臟中維他命D的生物活性形式<ref name="Adams&Hewison2010" />。

無論是在皮膚中合成還是透過攝取而成，維他命D於[[肝臟|肝臟]]中的位置25（分子的右上方）[[羥基化|羥基化]]，以形成25-羥基膽鈣化固醇（骨化二醇／25（OH）D）<ref name=Bikle>{{cite journal | vauthors = Bikle DD | title = Vitamin D metabolism, mechanism of action, and clinical applications | journal = Chemistry & Biology | volume = 21 | issue = 3 | pages = 319–29 | date = March 2014 | pmid = 24529992 | pmc = 3968073 | doi = 10.1016/j.chembiol.2013.12.016 }}</ref>。該反應由{{le|CYP2R1|CYP2R1}}這種人類基因[[微粒體|微粒體]]酶的產物催化，並由[[肝細胞|肝細胞]]表達<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Cheng JB, Levine MA, Bell NH, Mangelsdorf DJ, Russell DW | title = Genetic evidence that the human CYP2R1 enzyme is a key vitamin D 25-hydroxylase | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 101 | issue = 20 | pages = 7711–5 | date = May 2004 | pmid = 15128933 | pmc = 419671 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0402490101 | bibcode = 2004PNAS..101.7711C }}</ref>。當製成後，該產物會被釋放到[[血漿|血漿]]中，並與稱為{{le|維他命D結合蛋白|Vitamin D-binding protein}}的α-球蛋白載體蛋白結合<ref>{{cite book |vauthors=Laing CJ, Cooke NE |chapter=Section I: Ch. 8: Vitamin D Binding Protein |veditors=Feldman D, Glorieux FH, Pike JW |title=Vitamin D |volume=1 |publisher=Academic Press |edition=2 |year=2004 |isbn=978-0122526879 |pages=117–134 | chapter-url = {{google books |plainurl=y |id=5c66r0KrPUMC}}}}</ref>。骨化二醇被輸送到腎臟的近端小管，它在1-α位置（分子的右下角）被羥基化，形成骨化三醇（1,25-二羥基膽鈣化固醇，1,2,5（OH）<sub>2</sub>D）。骨化二醇向骨化三醇的轉化是通過酶[[CYP27B1|CYP27B1]]（25-羥基維他命D<sub>3</sub>1-α-羥化酶）催化，這是人類基因「CYP27B1」的產物。CYP27B1活性的增加是透過甲狀旁腺激素以及低鈣或低磷酸鹽的環境<ref name="Norman_2008"/><ref name="Adams&Hewison2010" />。

在腎臟的最後轉化步驟之後，骨化三醇會釋放到循環系統中。通過與維他命D結合蛋白的結合，骨化三醇被輸送到整個身體，包括腸道，腎臟和骨骼這些經典目標器官<ref name="River" />。骨化三醇是{{le|維他命D受體|Vitamin D receptor}}中最有效的天然[[配體|配體]]，它介導維他命D的大部分生理作用<ref name="Norman_2008"/><ref name="Adams&Hewison2010" />。除腎臟外，骨化三醇還由某些其他細胞合成，包括[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]中的[[单核细胞|單核白血球]]至[[巨噬細胞|巨噬細胞]]。當單核白血球跟巨噬細胞合成時，骨化三醇局部作為[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]，通過刺激[[先天免疫系統|先天免疫系統]]調節針對微生物入侵者的身體防禦<ref name="Adams&Hewison2010" />。

=== 鈍化 ===
骨化二醇和骨化三醇的活性可通過{{le|維他命D<sub>3</sub>24-羥化酶|Vitamin D3 24-hydroxylase}}的24位，分別形成分別骨鈣化醇（secalciferol）和（calcitetrol）進行羥基化來降低<ref name=Bikle/>。

=== 基質之間的差異 ===
維他命D<sub>2</sub>（麥角鈣化醇）和維他命D<sub>3</sub>（膽鈣化醇）具有如上所述的相似作用機理<ref name=Bikle/>。維他命D<sub>2</sub>產生的代謝物於英文名稱上有時以「er-」或「ergo」作為為前綴來命名，使其與基於D<sub>3</sub>的配對物作區分<ref name=nomen-d>{{cite journal | vauthors =  | title = IUPAC-IUB Joint Commission on Biochemical Nomenclature (JCBN): Nomenclature of vitamin D. Recommendations 1981 | journal = European Journal of Biochemistry | volume = 124 | issue = 2 | pages = 223–7 | date = May 1982 | pmid = 7094913 | doi = 10.1111/j.1432-1033.1982.tb06581.x }}</ref>。
* 由維他命D<sub>2</sub>產生的代謝物往往與維他命D結合蛋白的結合較差。
* 維他命D<sub>3</sub>可以通過[[CYP27A1|CYP27A1]]羥化為骨化二醇，但是維他命D<sub>2</sub>就不能。
* 麥角鈣化醇可以在位置24直接被羥基化。這種羥基化還導致更大程度的滅活：在24-羥基化作用後骨化三醇的活性降至原始水平的60％<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF, Kleiner-Bossaller A, Schnoes HK, Kasten PM, Boyle IT, DeLuca HF | title = 1,24,25-Trihydroxyvitamin D3. A metabolite of vitamin D3 effective on intestine | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 248 | issue = 19 | pages = 6691–6 | date = October 1973 | pmid = 4355503 }}</ref>，骨鈣三醇轉化為鈣鈣鈦礦的活性降低了10倍<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Horst RL, Reinhardt TA, Ramberg CF, Koszewski NJ, Napoli JL | title = 24-Hydroxylation of 1,25-dihydroxyergocalciferol. An unambiguous deactivation process | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 261 | issue = 20 | pages = 9250–6 | date = July 1986 | pmid = 3013880 }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
{{See|維他命#歷史}}

美國研究人員{{le|埃爾默·麥柯倫|Elmer McCollum}}和{{le|瑪格麗特·戴維斯|Marguerite Davis}}於1914年在[[魚肝油|魚肝油]]中發現了一種物質，後來稱為「[[維他命A|維他命A]]」<ref name="Wolf_2004"/>。英國醫生[[爱德华·梅兰比|爱德华·梅兰比]]留意到以魚肝油餵養的狗沒有發展成佝僂病，並得出結論指它是維他命A，或可以預防這種疾病的一個密切相關的因素。1922年，麥柯倫測試了改良的魚肝油，其中維他命A被破壞了<ref name="Wolf_2004"/>。經改良的魚肝油治癒了患病的狗隻，因此麥柯倫得出結論，魚肝油中治癒佝僂病的因素不同於維他命A<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/printarticle/239341 |title=Age-old children's disease back in force |publisher=Thestar.com |date=2007-07-25 |accessdate=2010-08-24 |archive-date=2008-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517044348/http://www.thestar.com/printArticle/239341 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jul/24/health/he-esoterica24 |author=Elena Conis |title=Fortified foods took out rickets |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2006-07-24 |accessdate=2010-08-24 |archive-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302045431/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jul/24/health/he-esoterica24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>McClean, Franklin C.; Budy, Ann M. "Vitamin A, Vitamin D, Cartilage, Bones, and Teeth" in Harris, Robert S. (1963). ''Vitamins and Hormones'', volume 21, pp. 51–52. London: Academic Press [http://books.google.com/books?id=gGb7vm2SapcC&lpg=PA52&pg=PA51#v=onepage Partial view] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=gGb7vm2SapcC&lpg=PA52&pg=PA51#v=onepage |date=20141001112247 }} at [[Google_Books|Google Books]].</ref>。他把它稱為維他命D，因為它是第四個被命名的維他命<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/printarticle/239341 |title=Age-old children's disease back in force |first=Suzanne |last=Carere |name-list-format=vanc |work=[[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]] |date=2007-07-25 |access-date=2010-08-24 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517044348/http://www.thestar.com/printArticle/239341 |archive-date=2008-05-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |vauthors=McClean FC, Budy AM |chapter=Vitamin A, Vitamin D, Cartilage, Bones, and Teeth |title=Vitamins and Hormones |chapterurl={{google books |plainurl=y |id=gGb7vm2SapcC  |pages = 51}} |date = 1964-01-28 | publisher = Academic Press | isbn = 978-0-12-709821-0 | volume = 21 | pages = 51–52}}</ref>。最初人們並未意識到，它與其他維他命不同，維他命D可以由人體透過暴露於紫外線下合成。

1925年，當研究人員利用光照射7-脫氫膽固醇時，確立利用光照射7-脫氫膽固醇時，會產生了一種[[親脂性|親脂性]]維他命（現在稱為維他命D<sub>3</sub>）<ref name="Wolf_2004"/>。{{le|阿爾弗雷德·法比安·赫斯|Alfred Fabian Hess}}指出：「光等於維他命D<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vitamind.ucr.edu/about/ |title=History of Vitamin D |publisher=University of California at Riverside |date=2011 |access-date=2014-05-09 |archive-date=2017-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016014311/http://vitamind.ucr.edu/about/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.beyonddiscovery.org/content/view.txt.asp?a=414 "Unraveling The Enigma Of Vitamin D"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beyonddiscovery.org/content/view.txt.asp?a=414 |date=20130204111737 }} [[United_States_National_Academy_of_Sciences|United States National Academy of Sciences]]</ref>。」德國[[哥廷根大学|格丁根大學]]的[[阿道夫·溫道斯|阿道夫·溫道斯]]，他於1928年因研究固醇的組成及其與維他命的關係而獲得[[诺贝尔化学奖|諾貝爾化學獎]]，以表彰其在研究固醇與維他命之間關係的工作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1928/windaus-bio.html |title=Adolf Windaus – Biography |publisher=Nobelprize.org |date=2010-03-25 |access-date=2010-03-25 |archive-date=2018-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724002502/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1928/windaus-bio.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1929年，位於倫敦漢普斯特德的{{le|國立醫學研究所（NIMR）|National Institute for Medical Research}}的一個小組正在研究目前尚未清楚的維他命D結構，以及類固醇的結構。他們跟[[約翰·伯頓·桑德森·霍爾丹|約翰·伯頓·桑德森·霍爾丹]]、[[J·D·伯納爾|J·D·伯納爾]]及[[多萝西·霍奇金|桃樂絲·霍奇金]]進行會議討論了可能的結構，這有助於使小組團結起來。X光晶體學分析顯示甾醇分子呈扁平狀，這跟溫道斯所領導的德國團隊提議的有所不同。1932年，奧托·羅森海姆（Otto Rosenheim）和哈羅德·金（Harold King）發表了一篇論文，提出了甾醇和膽汁酸的結構，這個論點立即被接受<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Rosenheim O, King H |title=The Ring-system of sterols and bile acids. Part II |journal=J. Chem. Technol. Biotechnol. |volume=51 |pages=954–7 |year=1932 |doi=10.1002/jctb.5000514702 |issue=47}}</ref>。團隊成員{{le|羅伯特·本尼迪·鮑迪永|Robert Benedict Bourdillon}}、奧托·羅森海姆、哈羅德·金及{{le|肯尼斯·卡洛|Kenneth Callow}}之間的非正式學術合作非常有成效，並導致維他命D的隔離和表徵的發現<ref>{{ cite journal | vauthors = Askew FA, Bourdillon RB, Bruce HM, Callow RK, ((St. L. Philpot J)), Webster TA | title = Crystalline Vitamin D |journal = Proceedings of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Containing Papers of a Biological Character |volume = 109 | issue = 764 | pages = 488–506 | doi = 10.1098/rspb.1932.0008 | year = 1932 | jstor=81571| doi-access = free }}</ref>。當時，[[英國醫學研究委員會|英國醫學研究委員會]]的政策不是針對專利發現，而是認為醫學研究的結果應該向所有人開放。在1930年代，溫道斯進一步闡明了維他命D的化學結構<ref name=Hirsch2011>{{cite book |author=Hirsch AL |chapter=Industrial aspects of vitamin D |title=Vitamin D |year=2011 |veditors=Feldman DJ, Pike JW, Adams JS |publisher=Academic Press  |pages = 73 | chapter-url ={{google books |plainurl=y |id=w7hMAFmsM84C  |pages = 73}} | isbn = 978-0-12-387035-3 }}</ref>。

1923年，[[威斯康辛大學麥迪遜分校|威斯康辛大學麥迪遜分校]]的美國生物化學家{{le|哈利·斯汀博克|Harry Steenbock}}的研究顯示，紫外線照射增加了食物和其他有機物質中維他命D的含量<ref name="isbn0-8047-4920-5">{{cite book |vauthors=Ziedonis AA, Mowery DC, Nelson RR, Bhaven NS |title=Ivory tower and industrial innovation: university-industry technology transfer before and after the Bayh-Dole Act in the United States |publisher=Stanford Business Books |year=2004 |pages=39–40 |isbn=978-0-8047-4920-6 |url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=sCscGlm2Q8YC  |pages = 39}} }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=Arvids A. Ziedonis; Mowery, David C.; Nelson, Richard R.; Bhaven N. Sampat |title=Ivory tower and industrial innovation: university-industry technology transfer before and after the Bayh-Dole Act in the United States |publisher=Stanford Business Books |location=Stanford, Calif |year=2004 |pages= [http://books.google.com/books?id=sCscGlm2Q8YC&pg=PA3939–40] |isbn=0-8047-4920-5}}</ref>。在照射囓齒動物的食物後，斯汀博克發現囓齒動物的佝僂病得到治癒。維他命D缺乏是已知佝僂病的已知病因。斯汀博克於是利用自己的$300美元為其發明申請了專利。他把其技術用於食物，最讓人難忘的是用於牛奶。他的專利於1945年到期時，佝僂病在美國幾乎被淘汰了<ref name="Marshall2010">{{cite book |first=James |last=Marshall | name-list-format = vanc |title=Elbridge a Stuart: Founder of Carnation Company |url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=6fICTwEACAAJ}}|date=September 2010|publisher=Kessinger Publishing|isbn=978-1-164-49678-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author = Marshall, James|year = 2005|title = Elbridge A. Stuart Founder of the Carnation Company|publisher = Kessinger Publishing|page = 235|isbn = 978-1417988839 }}</ref>。

1969年，在研究了腸道細胞的核碎片後，馬克·考斯勒（Mark Haussler）與{{le|安東尼·W·諾曼|Anthony W. Norman}}鑑定了一種稱為{{le|維他命D受體|Vitamin D receptor}}的維他命D特異性結合蛋白<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Haussler MR, Norman AW | title = Chromosomal receptor for a vitamin D metabolite | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 62 | issue = 1 | pages = 155–62 | date = January 1969 | pmid = 5253652 | pmc = 285968 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.62.1.155 | bibcode = 1969PNAS...62..155H }}</ref>。在1971–72年，維他命D進一步代謝以活性形式被發現。在肝臟中，維他命D被發現轉化為骨化二醇。骨化二醇然後被腎臟轉化為骨化三醇 — 維他命D於生物學上的活性形式<ref name="autogenerated2799" />。骨化三醇作為一種激素在血液中循環，調節血液中鈣和磷酸鹽的濃度，促進骨骼的健康生長和重塑。維他命D代謝物—骨化二醇和骨化三醇，分別由東尼·諾曼及其同事於{{le|赫克托·德盧卡|Hector DeLuca}}實驗室中的跟{{le|米高·F·霍利克|Michael F. Holick}}領導的競賽團隊於實驗中確定<ref name="pmid4323790">{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF, Schnoes HK, DeLuca HF | title = Identification of 1,25-dihydroxycholecalciferol, a form of vitamin D3 metabolically active in the intestine | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 68 | issue = 4 | pages = 803–4 | date = April 1971 | pmid = 4323790 | pmc = 389047 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.68.4.803 | bibcode = 1971PNAS...68..803H }}</ref><ref name="pmid4325863">{{cite journal | vauthors = Norman AW, Myrtle JF, Midgett RJ, Nowicki HG, Williams V, Popják G | s2cid = 35236666 | title = 1,25-dihydroxycholecalciferol: identification of the proposed active form of vitamin D3 in the intestine | journal = Science | volume = 173 | issue = 3991 | pages = 51–4 | date = July 1971 | pmid = 4325863 | doi = 10.1126/science.173.3991.51 | bibcode = 1971Sci...173...51N }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Holick MF, DeLuca HF, Avioli LV | title = Isolation and identification of 25-hydroxycholecalciferol from human plasma | journal = Archives of Internal Medicine | volume = 129 | issue = 1 | pages = 56–61 | date = January 1972 | pmid = 4332591 | doi = 10.1001/archinte.1972.00320010060005 }}</ref>。

== 科研 ==
維他命D缺乏症在歐洲人口中普遍存在著<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Cashman KD, Dowling KG, Škrabáková Z, Gonzalez-Gross M, Valtueña J, De Henauw S, Moreno L, Damsgaard CT, Michaelsen KF, Mølgaard C, Jorde R, Grimnes G, Moschonis G, Mavrogianni C, Manios Y, Thamm M, Mensink GB, Rabenberg M, Busch MA, Cox L, Meadows S, Goldberg G, Prentice A, Dekker JM, Nijpels G, Pilz S, Swart KM, van Schoor NM, Lips P, Eiriksdottir G, Gudnason V, Cotch MF, Koskinen S, Lamberg-Allardt C, Durazo-Arvizu RA, Sempos CT, Kiely M | display-authors = 6 | title = Vitamin D deficiency in Europe: pandemic? | journal = The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition | volume = 103 | issue = 4 | pages = 1033–44 | date = April 2016 | pmid = 26864360 | pmc = 5527850 | doi = 10.3945/ajcn.115.120873 }}</ref>。歐洲正在研究與疾病發生率和飲食建議、食物強化、維他命D補充和日間少量暴露於陽光下的相關政策來評估維他命D的攝入量<ref name=spiro/>。除了VDR激活外，各種不同的作用機制正在研究中，例如透過[[刺蝟信號通路|刺蝟]]的[[訊息傳遞_(生物)|生物訊息傳遞]]，那是一種有關激素的[[形態發生|形態發生]]<ref name=Sarkar2010 />。

關於維他命D干預益處的證據出現互相矛盾<ref name="pmid28163705">{{cite journal | vauthors = Dankers W, Colin EM, van Hamburg JP, Lubberts E | title = Vitamin D in Autoimmunity: Molecular Mechanisms and Therapeutic Potential | journal = Frontiers in Immunology | volume = 7 | issue =  | pages = 697 | year = 2016 | pmid = 28163705 | pmc = 5247472 | doi = 10.3389/fimmu.2016.00697 }}</ref>，有一種觀點認為日曬的每天攝入量為4,000-12,000個IU，同時血清中的25-羥基維他命D水平為40-80ng/mL<ref name="Heaney_Holick_2011"/>，而另一種觀點認為血清濃度高於50ng / mL是不合理的<ref name="Heaney_Holick_2011">{{cite journal | vauthors = Heaney RP, Holick MF | title = Why the IOM recommendations for vitamin D are deficient | journal = Journal of Bone and Mineral Research | volume = 26 | issue = 3 | pages = 455–7 | date = March 2011 | pmid = 21337617 | doi = 10.1002/jbmr.328 | s2cid = 41510449 }}</ref><ref name=holick2011 />。

截至2013年的證據，證據都不足以確定維他命D是否對癌症風險會有影響<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cancer.gov/about-cancer/causes-prevention/risk/diet/vitamin-d-fact-sheet#q4 |title=How is vitamin D being studied now in clinical cancer research? |publisher=National Cancer Institute, US National Institutes of Health |date=2013-10-21 |accessdate=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2015-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213152515/http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/factsheet/prevention/vitamin-D#q4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[國家衛生院_(美國)|美國國家衛生研究院]]的膳食補充劑辦公室於2014年建立了一項維他命D計劃，以追踪當時的研究並向消費者提供教育<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ods.od.nih.gov/Research/VitaminD.aspx |title=ODS Vitamin D Initiative |publisher=Office of Dietary Supplements, US National Institutes of Health |date=2014 |accessdate=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126003225/https://ods.od.nih.gov/Research/VitaminD.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們進一步指出：「這些作用的大多數證據來自體外、動物和流行病學研究，而不是被認為更具決定性的隨機臨床試驗。直至此類試驗進行之前，將會進行現有關於公共衛生和患者護理問題牽連證據的討論<ref name=NIH2016 />。」一些初步研究把低水平的維他命D與生命後期的疾病聯繫在一起<ref>{{Cite book |vauthors=Pyrżak B, Witkowska-Sędek E, Krajewska M, Demkow U, Kucharska AM |chapter=Metabolic and immunological consequences of vitamin D deficiency in obese children |volume=840 |pages=13–9 |year=2015 |pmid=25315624 |doi=10.1007/5584_2014_81 |isbn=978-3-319-10249-8 |series=Advances in Experimental Medicine and Biology |title=Body Metabolism and Exercise}}</ref>。一項綜合分析發現老年人的死亡率降低<ref name=Bj2014/>。另一項涵蓋超過350,000人的綜合分析得出結論，在未經揀選的社區居民中個人補充維他命D不會使骨骼（總骨折）或非骨骼結果（心肌梗塞、缺血性心臟病、中風、腦血管疾病、癌症）減少了15％以上，而且具有類似設計的進一步研究都不太可能改變這些結論<ref name=Futil2014/>。

2019年的綜合分析發現，同時服用鈣和維他命D可能會增加中風的風險<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Khan SU, Khan MU, Riaz H, Valavoor S, Zhao D, Vaughan L, Okunrintemi V, Riaz IB, Khan MS, Kaluski E, Murad MH, Blaha MJ, Guallar E, Michos ED | display-authors = 6 | title = Effects of Nutritional Supplements and Dietary Interventions on Cardiovascular Outcomes: An Umbrella Review and Evidence Map | journal = Annals of Internal Medicine | volume = 171 | issue = 3 | pages = 190–198 | date = August 2019 | pmid = 31284304 | pmc = 7261374 | doi = 10.7326/m19-0341 }}</ref>。另外，他們亦於2020年的審查中意識到，人們認識到越來越多的研究表明，維他命D在預防和治療1型和2型糖尿病、葡萄糖不耐症、高血壓、多發性硬化症和其他醫學疾病中可能發揮著某些作用。然而，他們得出的結論是，除了在骨骼健康方面有著更為積極的發現以外，現有證據都不足或太矛盾，以致無法確認維他命D在這些情況下的有效性<ref name="NIH-ODS-2020">{{cite web |title=Office of Dietary Supplements - Vitamin D |url=https://ods.od.nih.gov/factsheets/VitaminD-HealthProfessional/ |website=ods.od.nih.gov |accessdate=2020-10-31 |language=en |archive-date=2016-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231073744/https://ods.od.nih.gov/factsheets/VitaminD-HealthProfessional/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== COVID-19 ===
維他命D缺乏症已被證明可能會增加患上嚴重呼吸道感染的風險<ref name=bmj2017/>。在[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]期間，這在2020年引起了人們對該潛力重新產生興趣。一個對27項出版物的系統評價和綜合分析發現，維他命D缺乏症跟更高機會感染COVID-19的可能性並沒有關聯，但發現到維他命D缺乏症跟疾病的嚴重程度之間存在著正相關的關係，包括了住院率和死亡率的增加<ref name="pmid33146028">{{cite journal | vauthors = Pereira M, Dantas Damascena A, Galvão Azevedo LM, de Almeida Oliveira T, da Mota Santana J | title = Vitamin D deficiency aggravates COVID-19: systematic review and meta-analysis | journal = Critical Reviews in Food Science and Nutrition | pages = 1–9 | date = November 2020 | pmid = 33146028 | doi = 10.1080/10408398.2020.1841090 }}</ref>。

2020年6月，美國[[美國國立衛生研究院|美國國立衛生研究院]]發現沒有足夠的證據建議或反對使用維他命D補充劑作為專門預防或治療COVID-19<ref name="NIH2020-D-C19">{{Cite web|title=Vitamin D {{!}} Coronavirus Disease COVID-19|url=https://www.covid19treatmentguidelines.nih.gov/adjunctive-therapy/vitamin-d/|access-date=2020-10-03|website=COVID-19 Treatment Guidelines (US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention)|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127192830/https://www.covid19treatmentguidelines.nih.gov/adjunctive-therapy/vitamin-d/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，{{le|英國國家健康與護理卓越學院|National Institute for Health and Care Excellence}}發現沒有證據支持或反對服用維他命D補充劑為專門預防或治療COVID-19<ref name="NICE2020">{{cite web |title=Advisory statement on likely place in therapy {{!}} COVID-19 rapid evidence summary: vitamin D for COVID-19 {{!}} Advice {{!}} NICE |url=https://www.nice.org.uk/advice/es28/chapter/Advisory-statement-on-likely-place-in-therapy |website=www.nice.org.uk |access-date=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218103357/https://www.nice.org.uk/advice/es28/chapter/Advisory-statement-on-likely-place-in-therapy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這兩個組織都提出了一些建議，而這些建議是應繼續適用先前出於其他原因而補充維他命D建議（如骨骼和肌肉健康）。兩個組織都指出，由於COVID-19大流行期間的日照量較低，可能有更多的人需要補充劑<ref name="NIH2020-D-C19" /><ref name="NICE2020" />，而英國國民保健署（NHS）已為COVID-19高危人群免費提供每天維他命D補充劑<ref>{{cite web |title=Get vitamin D supplements if you're at high risk from coronavirus (COVID-19) |url=https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/coronavirus-covid-19/people-at-higher-risk/get-vitamin-d-supplements/ |website=nhs.uk |access-date=2020-11-30 |language=en |date=2020-11-27 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202090515/https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/coronavirus-covid-19/people-at-higher-risk/get-vitamin-d-supplements/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

COVID-19的主要併發症是[[急性呼吸窘迫症候群|急性呼吸窘迫綜合症]]（ARDS），可能是由於維他命D缺乏症而加劇<ref name="Quesada-Gomez">{{cite journal | vauthors = Quesada-Gomez JM, Entrenas-Castillo M, Bouillon R | title = Vitamin D receptor stimulation to reduce acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS) in patients with coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 infections: Revised Ms SBMB 2020_166 | journal = The Journal of Steroid Biochemistry and Molecular Biology | volume = 202 | pages = 105719 | date = September 2020 | pmid = 32535032 | doi = 10.1016/j.jsbmb.2020.105719 | pmc = 7289092 }}</ref>，但這個關聯並不明確與冠狀病毒感染有關<ref name="Quesada-Gomez"/>。不同國家將於2020年進行許多試驗，以探討使用維他命D作為預防和治療SARS-CoV-2感染的潛力<ref name="Quesada-Gomez"/><ref name="vitD-clintrials"/>。

